            sourceSnippet: 'Saudi FM concludes China visit amid Trump-MBS friction: What to know — Al-Monitor, 2 Juli 2026',
            source2: 'Al Arabiya English',
            sourceUrl2: 'https://english.alarabiya.net/News/saudi-arabia/2026/06/30/top-saudi-diplomat-in-china-to-discuss-regional-international-issues',
            sourceSnippet2: 'Saudi FM discusses regional, international developments with China\'s VP in Beijing — Al Arabiya English, 30 Juni 2026',
            source3: 'Anadolu Agency',
            sourceUrl3: 'https://www.aa.com.tr/en/middle-east/saudi-foreign-minister-to-visit-china-amid-renewed-us-iran-tensions/3980820',
